title: 'Bindaaz night'
body: 'The Whisper Bindazzz Night Sanitary Pads have truly impressed me! This pack of 16 thin pads XXL+ in size provides superior protection with zero leaks. They are not only 60% longer and wider but also incredibly comfortable to wear throughout the night. I appreciate the extra coverage which gives me peace of mind while sleeping. These pads are a game-changer for overnight protection and I highly recommend them for anyone seeking a reliable and comfortable solution during their menstrual cycle.'
